high_descs: Head straight to stand beside the two black bar stools, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the butter knife from the counter.
Turn left to move around the counter and then go right to stand in front of the counter to the right of the stove.
Use the knife to slice the loaf of bread on the counter.
Turn left towards the sink, and then head left again to the microwave.
Place the knife inside the microwave.
Turn around and return to the sliced bread to the right of the stove.
Pick up a slice of bread from the counter.
Turn and carry the bread to the microwave.
Place the bread in the microwave and then remove once heated.
Take a step to the left to carry the bread to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the bread on the shelf by the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Refrigerate a slice of warm bread.

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room and turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Walk around the counter to face the bread on the counter.
Cut the bread on the counter into slices.
Turn around and walk forward to face the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the bread on the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Turn around and walk forward to face the microwave.
Heat the bread in the microwave and remove it.
Take a step to the left to face the fridge.
Place the bread slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To heat a bread slice plus store it in the fridge.

high_descs: Go forward, turn left in front of the counter
Pick up the knife on the counter
Move around the counter and go to the right of the stove
Slice the bread on the counter
Turn left, go forward, turn left, go to the microwave
Put the knife in the microwave
Turn left, go forward, turn left, go to the counter
Pick up a bread slice from the counter
Turn left, go forward, turn left, go to the microwave
Put the bread slice in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the bread slice from the microwave
Move a bit to the left to the front of the fridge
Put the bread slice in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Slice a bread, cook a slice of bread and put it in the fridge
